This year he had another of the same quality.
"We just signed a contract with a hotel in Ostrova U Tise where we sold our franchise concept and other candidates for the Pytloun hotel franchise have come forward", the number 1 of last year's entrepreneurs.
"And for the sale of the license to operate a large-scale hotel, the winning of the Entrepreneur of the Year competition has served well", adds Pytloun with appreciation.
The victory brought him more popularity and being known in Liberec and its surroundings.
"People recognized me on the streets, often complimented me, and I must say it was very pleasant", he recalls.
He encourages all those who are trying to do something to take part in this competition.
It's not necessary to win, but any opportunity to be visible is good.
He says he uses to this day his contacts and knowledge which he could not have obtained otherwise.
"With those I met through the competition I began to maintain regular business relations.
He said that the reputation linked to success had an impact on employees as well.
