At the Land Fund in Plzen, police made arrests during a public tender
The anti-corruption police have been making arrests at the Land Fund building in Plzen in recent days.
Detectives have handcuffed local real estate developer G. Lubos.
The Commission has made every effort to correctly handle a public tender for the settlement of a claim for restitution in such a way that the proposed land is obtained by a determined candidate.
