The stakes are clear.
And it would be a shame not to hear it.
It is not just a question of bringing the government deficit back to 3% in 2013.
What we're being asked to do is much harder.
And what he should never do in these circumstances is to deceive ourselves.
I hope that the current turmoil will bring us a greater peace.
And we'll take the opportunity we've been given, until the spring of 2013.
